Git-commit: 6c387ab20db15f2bd448f7c508e2638101b16ea1
Subject: [PATCH] Btrfs: fix missing error handler if submiting re-read
 bio fails

We forgot to free failure record and bio after submitting re-read bio failed,
fix it.

Signed-off-by: Miao Xie <miaox@cn.fujitsu.com>
Signed-off-by: Chris Mason <clm@fb.com>
Signed-off-by: David Sterba <dsterba@suse.cz>
---
 fs/btrfs/extent_io.c |    5 +++++
 1 file changed, 5 insertions(+)

--- a/fs/btrfs/extent_io.c
+++ b/fs/btrfs/extent_io.c
@@ -2377,6 +2377,11 @@ static int bio_readpage_error(struct bio
 	ret = tree->ops->submit_bio_hook(inode, read_mode, bio,
 					 failrec->this_mirror,
 					 failrec->bio_flags, 0);
+	if (ret) {
+		free_io_failure(inode, failrec, 0);
+		bio_put(bio);
+	}
+
 	return ret;
 }
 
